appeng.api.storage.data

Interface IAEFluidStack

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IAEStack<IAEFluidStack>

    public interface IAEFluidStack
extends IAEStack<IAEFluidStack>
    An alternate version of FluidStack for AE to keep tabs on things easier, and to support larger storage. stackSizes of getFluidStack will be capped. You may hold on to these if you want, just make sure you let go of them when your not using them. Don't Implement. Construct with AEApi.instance().storage().getStorageChannel( IFluidStorageChannel.class).createStack( FluidStack )
